  <string name="basic_hint">This sample showcases the basics usages of the adapter. The adapter has a simple divider decoration, which adapts well with different configuration.</string>
  <string name="advanced_hint">This sample showcases the adapter with multiple view types and multiple sections. Each view type has its own span count, swipe direction, drag directions etc.,  </string>
  <string name="selection_hint">This sample showcases the selection feature of the library. Tap an item to toggle the selection. Each section has its own selection mode ie., single, multiple etc., Change the selection mode inside the configuration screen.</string>
  <string name="expansion_hint">This sample showcases the expansion feature of the library. You can expand individual item or a section. Change the expansion mode inside the configuration screen.</string>
  <string name="decoration_hint">This sample showcases the powerful decoration api of the library. Decorations are drawn for each item and for whole sections as well. For example, divider is drawn between each section and between each item.</string>
  <string name="tree_section_hint">This sample showcases usage the TreeSection from the library. With TreeSection you can display a nested list of data ie., comments, threads. You can change the decoration from configuration screen.</string>
  <string name="news_feed_hint">This sample showcases a mock news feed screen.</string>
